        If ``True``, all metadata (EXIF, ICC profiles, XMP, etc.) is removed from the
        image once the transposition has been applied. If ``False`` (default), only
        the EXIF Orientation tag is removed and other metadata is preserved.
    :param transform_callback: A callable. Keyword-only argument.
        If given, it is called with the EXIF Orientation value and must return the
